# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
#  OQS-Nginx KD Protocol Benchmarking — TLS 1.3 Configuration (TEMPLATE)
#  Image: openquantumsafe/nginx:latest
#  Signature: ECDSA P-256 (classical)  |  KEM: rendered by orchestrator
#
#  Do not edit nginx.conf directly — it is generated from this template.
#  Placeholder __KEM_GROUP__ is substituted by run_matrix.sh before each run.
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

worker_processes  1;    # Match CPU limit in docker-compose
error_log         /dev/stderr warn;
pid               /opt/nginx/nginx.pid;

events {
    worker_connections 1024;
    use                epoll;
    multi_accept       on;
}

http {
    include       /opt/nginx/conf/mime.types;
    default_type  application/octet-stream;

    # ── Logging: include $ssl_curve for handshake group visibility ──────
    log_format kd_fmt '$remote_addr - [$time_local] "$request" '
                      '$status $body_bytes_sent '
                      'ssl_protocol=$ssl_protocol '
                      'ssl_cipher=$ssl_cipher '
                      'ssl_curve=$ssl_curve '        # <-- KEY FIELD
                      'rt=$request_time';

    access_log logs/access.log kd_fmt;

    sendfile    on;
    tcp_nopush  on;
    keepalive_timeout  65;

    # ── HTTPS Server Block ──────────────────────────────────────────────
    server {
        listen       4433 ssl;
        server_name  oqs-nginx;

        # Certificate chain (ECDSA P-256 signed) — held constant across
        # all KEM groups intentionally; isolates KEM cost, not signature cost.
        ssl_certificate      /certs/server.crt;
        ssl_certificate_key  /certs/server.key;

        # ── TLS Protocol: strict TLS 1.3 only ───────────────────────────
        ssl_protocols  TLSv1.3;

        # ── KEM Group advertised to clients — rendered per matrix run ───
        #  Valid values used by run_matrix.sh:
        #    classical : X25519
        #    hybrid    : X25519MLKEM768
        #    pure-pq   : MLKEM768
        ssl_ecdh_curve  __KEM_GROUP__;

        # ── Session settings ────────────────────────────────────────────
        ssl_session_cache    shared:SSL:10m;
        ssl_session_timeout  10m;
        ssl_session_tickets  off;  # Disable for consistent full handshakes

        # ── HSTS (informational for PoC) ────────────────────────────────
        add_header Strict-Transport-Security "max-age=300" always;
        add_header X-KD-Group               "$ssl_curve" always;

        # ── Static content ──────────────────────────────────────────────
        root   /opt/nginx/html;
        index  index.html;

        location / {
            try_files $uri $uri/ =404;
        }

        # ── Health check endpoint ───────────────────────────────────────
        location /health {
            return 200 "OK ssl_curve=$ssl_curve\n";
            add_header Content-Type text/plain;
        }
    }
}
